description: For sale: $690,000. Family retreat  with 10 individual cabins, dining hall, shower-house, large garage, outdoor hot tub, sauna and boat equipment shed. Wilderness setting on a small pristine lake in Superior National Forest. Perfect for large family gatherings year round and has direct access to the 30km Flathorn/Gegoka xc ski trail system. 1,400+ feet of shoreline on sandy bottom Lake Gegoka. Only 6 other private parcels on the lake and the rest is National Forest land. Too many improvements in the past 12 years to list here. Contact us to get the list. Has been run as a ma and pa resort for 100 years and still can be if you choose.

For sale: $70,000. Up North retreat.  Are you looking for a place to enjoy all the recreational activities that northern MN can offer?  This is the place for you. Easily accessible.  Being directly off Hwy 1 makes this an easy place to open up when arriving from out of town for fun.  The original house was demolished last fall and this 2005 mobile home was set up. Recently remodeled with new cabinets, granite counters, newer appliances, spray foam insulation in walls and underneath.  New hot water heater in fall of 2019.  Custom Bali blinds throughout. Keypad entry makes it easy to allow friends to stay.   Septic was tested in 2018 and compliant.  Well. electricity. Camper plug in on new electrical meter stand so your friends can hook right up.  24x24 garage to store your toys. Direct access to the snowmobile trail from the edge of the yard. Surrounded by 1000's of acres of federal forest will make it seem like you own the woods.  100's of lakes within minutes.  Would sell furnished.

description: For sale: $340,000. Beautiful Voyageur log cabin/home built with 10" logs.  255 ft on the Stony River.  3.3 acres.  The cabin has 2 bedrooms, a 3/4 bath,  spacious kitchen/dining area/living room with large windows providing natural light & great views.  Stainless steel appliances, hickory cabinetry, Italian porcelain tile.  Patio doors in the dining area leading to the deck overlooking the river.  Free standing wood stove in the living room.  Wood floors in the living area & bedrooms. 3 finished living levels.   Finished loft with access to  the upper deck.  Finished walk-out basement, Recreation room  with attached studio/den. Detached 4 car garage.  Guest cabin.    Peaceful setting with magnificent pines and the river frontage.  Good walleye fishing. & propane fireplace. Year around access. Four season home.  Just a short distance to Ely, the BWCAW Duluth & Two Harbors.  Call for additional details.

description: For sale: $175,000. Well maintained 4 bedroom home with a large kitchen, center island and dining room, spacious enough for a large family or gatherings of several people. description: For sale: $199,000. Looking to run a business in "God's Country"?  Here is your chance!  This well established Cafe has been doing business for decades and is ready for the next owner to make this business their own.  This property includes a 2 bedroom 1 bath heated cabin that can be rented for extra income and is located right in the middle of popular recreational opportunities. Lakes, campgrounds, public land and atv/snowmobile/cross country ski trails are all nearby and keep a steady flow of potential clientele around. The property also includes an additional 2 bedroom 1 bath apartment that is currently being used by the owners as well as a 30' x 60' storage building that was the old bait shop.  All equipment in the kitchen is included in the sale. Make the trip out today and start dreaming of the possibilities of your own business!
